en_790887_0	COLOMBO (News 1st): The Department of Prisons is to install special security devices to the prisons.
en_790887_1	Commissioner General of Prisons, T.M.J.W. Tennakoon said that the decision was taken in order to tackle illegal activities and ensure security within the prison walls.
en_790887_2	The security devices will be installed in 18 prisons including Boosa, Galle, Magazine, Dumbara and Kalutara where notorious criminals are housed.
en_790887_3	The estimated budget for the systems is Rs.
en_790887_4	480 million.
